title: Liberty hosts regional flight competition, wins for 11th straight year (Liberty University)
text: ( Source : Liberty University ) October 19 , 2015 : Liberty University News Service The Liberty University School of Aeronautics hosted the National Intercollegiate Flying Association ( NIFA ) Region X competition for the first time, Oct. 14-17,
